.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-SPENDABLE-PCT-RANGE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-spendable-pct-range \- FEAT-2800 channel-spendable-pct-range
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-spendable-pct-range
.SH DESCRIPTION
Range (max minus min) of spendable balance percentage across channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2800).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBspendable_pct_range\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
